經濟思想史(1)








開課班級

經濟學系四年B班     ˇ必修    □選修


學分數

2學分    2小時      預備知識：經濟學 


授課方式

ˇ口頭講授   ˇ分組討論   □媒體教學   □上機實習   
□其他（請詳述於後）


教學目標

中文

本課程介紹經濟學派的演進，討論重要學派代表人物的思想內涵，進而幫助同學對於經濟學理論成立的時代背景有深入的認知。


英文

The main goal in this class is to discuss the economic thinking of some of the greatest minds of the modern era, such as Adam Smith, John Stuart Mill, David Hume, Karl Marx, Thomas Malthus, and John Maynard Keynes. Learning about the lives and ideas of these people is valuable in itself. But this course will also serve other purposes. It will be a way of acquiring a deeper understanding of economics for those who have taken economics courses before.


教材課本

【遵守智慧財產權觀念，不得非法影印】
All materials are available on my website.


參考書籍

【遵守智慧財產權觀念，不得非法影印】
 


